Description: A set of functions for estimating cognitive diagnosis models using a stochastic EM algorithm. The package provides parameter estimation and classification procedures based on the implementation described in the paper A Stochastic Expectation-Maximization Algorithm for High Dimensional  Cognitive Diagnosis Models.
